data.description: Located on a quiet cul-de-sac on one acre in Santa Ynez, you will find this quality four bedroom home with mountain views, privacy, and upgraded features.  Close to Finley Farms produce stand in the agricultural area of the valley, yet close to schools and shopping, this location is ideal for a country feel while being close to town. You are welcomed with wood floors, picture windows, a wet bar, office/bedroom, family room, and an updated spacious kitchen with island, and a screened outdoor patio.  Remodeled in 2009 and 2017, you will enjoy the the upgraded features inside and entertaining your guests on the large patio with an outdoor fireplace and BBQ.  Enjoy summer inside with two air conditioning zones, owned solar panels, and the shaded back yard by the white oaks and sycamore trees.
